Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:05.76,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}不要放開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.95,0:23:07.39,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}不要遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:10.92,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}我一直都在等待著你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:15.74,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}這閃閃發光的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:22.84,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}我會小心翼翼的包起來 並送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:25.57,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}你在那裡等著
